title: Strengthen Your Inner Man | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Strengthen Your Inner Man | Victoria Osteen
description:
The presence of God wants to fill us with new strength each day. When you make it a habit to renew and strengthen your inner man, your life will be transformed for the better. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
